At lunchtime, you can not miss our exclusive restaurant, 99 Sushi Bar, with its delicious, innovative and traditional Japanese cuisine.

NH Sanvy hotel offers 146 elegant and modern rooms equipped with all amenities, such as wooden floors, private bathroom, hair dryer, satellite TV and air conditioning.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>SurroundingArea</Type><Text>The hotel's excellent location will allow you enjoy the best that Spain's capital has to offer. This comfortable hotel is situated in the 'Barrio de Salamanca' district, one of Madrid's most aristocratic neighbourhoods, close the Plaza de Colon and the Paseo de la Castellana.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>RoomTypes</Type><Text>Standard Room - Kick off your shoes and get comfortable in our 18-square meter Standard Rooms. Wood floors, warm colors, and amenities such as AC, heat, minibar, safe, room service, flat-screen satellite TV, and free Wi-Fi Internet access will make you feel at home.</Text></Description><Amenity><Code>CoffeeTeaMaker</Code><Text>Tea and Coffee maker</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Safe</Code><Text>Safe</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>HandicapAccessible</Code><Text>Handicap accessible</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>TVInRoom</Code><Text>TV in room</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>OutdoorPool</Code><Text>Outdoor swimming pool</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>MiniBarInRoom</Code><Text>Mini-bar</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>RoomService</Code><Text>Room service</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>HairDryer</Code><Text>Hair dryer</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>MoneyExchange</Code><Text>Money exchange</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Bar</Code><Text>Bar</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>ReceptionArea</Code><Text>Reception Area</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>CheckIn24hr</Code><Text>24hr. CheckIn</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Reception24hr</Code><Text>24hr. Reception</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>CloakRoom</Code><Text>Cloak Room</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Lift</Code><Text>Lift</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>ConferenceRoom</Code><Text>Conference Room</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code